{"ID":"20231124113627-30glybk","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"icon":"1f4a5","id":"20231124113627-30glybk","title":"Sidecar模式","updated":"20231124113928"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231124113629-mh41kcy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-mh41kcy","updated":"20231124113648"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Sidecar模式是一种在微服务架构中常见的设计模式，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"它通过将负载均衡逻辑与服务实例隔离，使用一个独立的代理（称为Sidecar）来处理流量的路由和负载均衡。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这个Sidecar代理与每个服务实例部署在同一个主机或容器中，并与其共享网络环境。"}]},{"ID":"20231124113629-9vniuhi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-9vniuhi","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面是Sidecar模式的主要特点和工作原理："}]},{"ID":"20231124113629-rd6shhu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-rd6shhu","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"特点："}]},{"ID":"20231124113629-dkc96ll","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-dkc96ll","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231124113629-4b90n0s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-4b90n0s","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231124113629-m9h6wjn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-m9h6wjn","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解耦负载均衡：通过将负载均衡逻辑放置在Sidecar代理中，可以将负载均衡与服务实例解耦，使得服务实例只需专注于处理自身的业务逻辑。"}]}]},{"ID":"20231124113629-h9l9ffu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-h9l9ffu","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231124113629-gqalnok","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-gqalnok","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"灵活性：Sidecar代理可以独立于服务实例进行部署、升级和扩缩容，不会对服务实例产生影响。"}]}]},{"ID":"20231124113629-9f1scxb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-9f1scxb","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231124113629-eeoe2bo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-eeoe2bo","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"支持多语言和多框架：不同的服务实例可以使用不同的编程语言和框架，而Sidecar代理可以提供统一的负载均衡能力。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20231124113629-wwxngiq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-wwxngiq","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"工作原理："}]},{"ID":"20231124113629-jjcj4mp","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-jjcj4mp","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231124113629-64vnw2e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-64vnw2e","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231124113629-yiemicb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-yiemicb","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注册和发现：每个服务实例通过服务注册将自己的信息注册到服务注册中心（如Consul），包括主机地址和端口号。"}]}]},{"ID":"20231124113629-gdo72f6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-gdo72f6","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231124113629-5r0su81","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-5r0su81","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Sidecar代理：在每个服务实例所在的主机或容器中部署一个Sidecar代理，它与服务实例共享网络环境。"}]}]},{"ID":"20231124113629-88mj18b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-88mj18b","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231124113629-mva8l0r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-mva8l0r","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"负载均衡：Sidecar代理从服务注册中心获取服务实例信息，并根据负载均衡策略选择一个合适的实例。它将接收到的流量路由至选定的实例。"}]}]},{"ID":"20231124113629-nk9i3ds","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-nk9i3ds","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231124113629-895wsqp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-895wsqp","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"监测和健康检查：Sidecar代理会监测服务实例的健康状态，并通过服务注册中心更新服务实例的健康状态信息。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20231124113629-f1ghd5c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113629-f1ghd5c","updated":"20231124113629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Sidecar模式可以提供一种灵活且可扩展的负载均衡方案，同时保持了微服务的独立性和可维护性。它使得服务实例无需关注负载均衡的具体实现细节，降低了服务实例的复杂性。同时，Sidecar代理可以提供更多的功能，如安全认证、流量监控等，以增强整个微服务架构的功能和可靠性。"}]},{"ID":"20231124113853-xcnhrya","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231124113853-xcnhrya","updated":"20231124113916"}}]}